Description
************
Increases without any apparent loss of image quality.
PhotoZoom is a sophisticated tool, by using different techniques, is capable of enlarging an image without causing the typical loss of quality.
You have ten nine resizing methods different adjustment methods applied on the resized to get the best result possible.
Although not its only use, you could say that is mainly focused to be used prior to printing, as it allows to easily select the final size of the enlarged image in millimeters, centimeters, inches, pixels or percentage of increase, indicating also dots per inch.
In short, PhotoZoom is a very specific and powerful utility to enhance any image, which could be broadly defined as a sophisticated interpolation, and get really very satisfactory results.
